# Atlas Web3 Infrastructure

Developer APIs for accessing Aptos blockchain data.

## Overview

Atlas Web3 Infrastructure provides developer-friendly APIs that allow applications to easily access and process data from the Aptos blockchain.

The goal of the project is to simplify blockchain development by offering reliable data pipelines and indexing tools.

## Features

- Aptos blockchain indexing
- REST APIs for developers
- scalable data pipelines
- developer SDK tools

## Use Cases

- blockchain explorers
- DeFi platforms
- NFT marketplaces
- Web3 applications

## Tech Stack

- Aptos
- Node.js
- Express
- decentralized storage integrations

## Project Status

Prototype stage.

Currently testing data indexing pipelines and building developer APIs.

